## PROJECT IDENTITY

A personal, single-user job and freelance finder for one software engineer
in Hyderabad, India. Not a product. Not SaaS. One person uses this forever.

Stack: Node.js 20 + Express + MongoDB + Gemini 1.5 Flash
Language: TypeScript only (.ts files)
Database: MongoDB local — mongodb://localhost:27017/jobsearch
Server port: 5000

