## TYPESCRIPT STANDARDS

- All interfaces prefixed with I — IProfile, IJob, IBookmark, IAiCache
- interface for object shapes. type for unions and aliases only.
- No any — use unknown and narrow it, or define the proper interface
- Every exported function must have a JSDoc comment with @param and @returns
- Shared interfaces defined in their respective model files — no separate types/ folder

---

## CODE STANDARDS

- async/await everywhere — no .then().catch() chains
- Every async route handler and service function wrapped in try/catch
- console.log for info, console.error for errors — no logging library
- 2-space indentation
- Single quotes for strings
- No semicolons

