## API RESPONSE SHAPE — ALWAYS THIS, NO EXCEPTIONS

```typescript
// Success
{ success: true, data: T }

// Error
{ success: false, error: { code: string, message: string } }
```

HTTP codes: 200 success, 201 created, 400 bad input,
404 not found, 429 rate limited, 500 server error.
Never expose raw Mongoose errors or Gemini SDK errors to the client.

