## EXTERNAL DATA SOURCES

Remotive:   GET https://remotive.com/api/remote-jobs?category=software-dev&limit=50
Arbeit Now: GET https://www.arbeitnow.com/api/job-board-api
Both are free. No API keys needed.

Remotive field mapping to IJob:
  id                         → externalId (prefix with 'remotive_')
  url                        → url
  title                      → title
  company_name               → company
  company_logo               → companyLogo
  description                → description
  tags                       → tags
  salary                     → salary
  candidate_required_location → location
  publication_date           → postedAt
  source                     → 'remotive'
  isRemote                   → true (always for Remotive)

Arbeit Now field mapping to IJob:
  slug         → externalId (prefix with 'arbeitnow_')
  url          → url
  title        → title
  company_name → company
  description  → description
  tags         → tags
  location     → location
  remote       → isRemote
  created_at   → postedAt
  source       → 'arbeitnow'

Dedup strategy: Job.bulkWrite() with updateOne + filter on externalId + upsert: true

